## Phase 2: Data Infrastructure

### 2.1 Create `clawd\data\client-activity.json`
Sparse overlay pattern - only clients with actual activity data:

```json
{
  "lastUpdated": "2026-01-27T12:00:00Z",
  "clients": {
    "endres-emily": {
      "pipeline": { "stage": "active-client", "stageEnteredDate": "2025-06-15" },
      "lastContact": "2025-12-01",
      "nextAction": "PAW form follow-up (6+ weeks overdue)",
      "nextActionDate": "2026-01-28",
      "annualReview": { "anniversaryDate": "2025-06-15", "nextDue": "2026-04-15" }
    },
    "schmidt-ben": {
      "pipeline": { "stage": "illustration", "stageEnteredDate": "2026-01-26" },
      "lastContact": "2026-01-26",
      "nextAction": "Guardian Life DR comparison illustrations",
      "nextActionDate": "2026-01-31"
    },
    "palumbo-dean": {
      "pipeline": { "stage": "underwriting", "stageEnteredDate": "2026-01-20" },
      "lastContact": "2026-01-26",
      "nextAction": "Oncologist info for Lafayette underwriting",
      "nextActionDate": "2026-01-31"
    }
  }
}
```

Seed with the 3-5 clients mentioned in MEMORY.md and daily notes that have known activity.

### 2.2 Update `clawd\data\CLIENT_DB_README.md`
Add pipeline stage definitions:

| Stage | Description | Stale After |
|-------|-------------|-------------|
| lead | New contact, not qualified | 14 days |
| byob-sent | BYOB book link sent | 14 days |
| byob-read | Confirmed they read BYOB | 7 days |
| intro-call | 30-min intro scheduled/completed | 7 days |
| design-meeting | Policy design session | 7 days |
| application | Application submitted | 3 days |
| underwriting | In review | 60 days |
| issued | Policy issued, awaiting funding | 30 days |
| active-client | Funded and active | 90 days (touchpoint) |
| inactive | Went cold or declined | terminal |

Document the sparse overlay pattern and how client-activity.json relates to clients.json.

### 2.3 Extend `clawd\memory\heartbeat-state.json`
Add fields to existing file:
```json
{
  "lastChecks": { "email": ..., "calendar": ..., "weather": ... },
  "lastFactExtraction": ...,
  "lastWeeklySynthesis": ...,
  "lastClawdHubScan": ...,
  "lastMorningBriefing": null,
  "lastFollowUpDigest": null,
  "lastEmailScan": null,
  "lastEveningRecap": null,
  "lastClientReview": null,
  "lastNotionSync": null
}
```

